title.rendered: Tromso Compact workstation with white legs, stylish complementing drawer and open storage compartment – home office

content.rendered:
Our Tromso Compact workstation with white legs, stylish complementing drawer and open storage compartment is perfect for the home office!

Made with 15mm Melamine wood effect laminate and a steel frame. 

Single underdesk drawer and open storage compartment.

Assembly required. 3 year warranty. Price is for desk only.
